Paper: hep-th/9810057

Date: 1998-10-08

Title: Singular Non-Abelian Toda Theories

Authors: J.F.Gomes, F.E. Mendon\c{c}a da Silveira, G.M. Sotkov and A.H.

ZimermanComments: Latex, 12 pages

The algebraic conditions that specific gauged G/H-WZW model have to satisfyin order to give rise to Non-Abelian Toda models with singular metric with orwithout torsion are found. The classical algebras of symmetries correspondingto grade one rank 2 and 3 singular NA-Toda models are derived.